      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like putting myself through this every day is somehow selfish... like i'm forcing them to watch me fade away. you mentioned stepping away... do you really think they'd be better off if they didn't have to worry about me anymore? if i just... wasn't an issue for them to manage?",
